snippet.title: PAX East 2016 Super Senso Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
** WE'RE GOING TO PAX EAST...GET EXCITED! To celebrate this momentous occasion, GungHo Online Entertainment America and TURBO have put together this awesome Super Senso game trailer for your enjoyment.  GET HYPED! **

Super Senso is a FREE synchronous, turn-based action strategy game designed for competitive PvP play.  Collect and unleash game changing Senso Mechs!  Build a smash-up corp army of rage filled zombies, stealth ninjas, and dinosaurs to crush your enemies!  Outplay, outsmart and obliterate your enemies!
